<paragraph base="F16130925" principles="no" id="IFRS12_B16"><paranum>B16</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 12"/><data name="paranum" value="B16"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS12_P0295">An entity shall disclose, in aggregate, the carrying amount of its interests in all individually immaterial <xref base="F16124099" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0021">joint ventures<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0211"/></ph></xref> or <xref base="F16124075" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0016">associates<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0018"/></ph></xref> that are accounted for using the <xref base="F16124092" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0018">equity method<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0105"/></ph></xref>. An entity shall also disclose separately the aggregate amount of its share of those joint ventures&#x2019; or associates&#x2019;:</p><ol base="F16130927" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS12_L0048"><li id="IFRS12_B16_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F16130929" id="IFRS12_P0296">profit or loss from continuing operations.</p>       </li><li id="IFRS12_B16_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F16130931" id="IFRS12_P0297">post&#x2011;tax profit or loss from discontinued operations.</p>       </li><li id="IFRS12_B16_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="F16130933" id="IFRS12_P0298">other comprehensive income.</p>       </li><li id="IFRS12_B16_d"><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p base="F16130935" id="IFRS12_P0299">total comprehensive income.</p>       </li></ol><p base="F16130936" id="IFRS12_P0300">An entity provides the disclosures separately for joint ventures and associates.</p></body></paragraph>